# pytest-params

[![image](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pytest_params.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pytest_params)

Simplified pytest test case parameters.

----

## Installation

```
$ pip install pytest-params
```

## Examples
pytest native:
```python
@pytest.mark.parametrize('a', [1, 2, 3])
def test_foo(a):
    ...

```

